0.text: Nanugo kiital mai ciki daidai be nyalande be ta'eni jaumu aibe haqqi mako wadugo kiital lau.

1.text: Be fajira seɗɗa hande, hendu man ɗonno fufa be doggudu yottan kilomita 83 kala hawa Sali fu, diga ɓawo wari usti.

2.text: Kuje manga wooni ha der ko tarnata ii’amji mberde on yaara ta ii’am.

3.text: Di site je web do nangi hakkile himɓe bui, balle hedi jangirde.

4.text: Tarol wuro buri hoyugo to on do duudi, to an tan on ko be sobajo gotel, habdu a fotta be himbe fere se on hauta hore mon bana himbe nai yahugo jego jam chede kala goddo fu hoya.

5.text: Footoo film na'ura hoto ji fere do naftiran kala 6 be 6 cm, de'iddo ma jankiraadum 56 be 56 mm.

6.text: A wada bo a joga bindi no be watta kujeji be no be hebata mo yobatama to kuje vonni be ma.

7.text: A hebbina saare ma be kurugo kafe be fajjiri be bo'o saayi chamomile be jemma.

8.text: Kankara na deydey ba ; tekkugo baabal watan jogga tan be hakkilo, be to salitini ɗum wartan du jippita je kankaraji may.

9.text: Ceede nastata do sendi iri ha leddi feere feere, bo ko be jabata na iri gotel ba ha leddi feere feere.
